<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>BuildLink - 合作夥伴專區</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #004d99; color: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.5em; }
        .module-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
        .module-list li { background-color: #e6f7ff; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 5px solid #007bff; }
        .logout-link { margin-top: 30px; display: block; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>歡迎回來，夥伴：{{partnerId}}</h1>
        <p>您已成功進入 BuildLink 合作夥伴專屬介面。</p>
    </div>

    <h2>可用功能模組</h2>
    <ul class="module-list">
        {{#modules}}
        <li><a href="{{link}}">{{name}}</a></li>
        {{/modules}}
    </ul>

    <a href="/logout" class="logout-link">登 出 系統</a>
</body>
</html>